{
  "stem": "26983.12",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 67.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we children knew it's dangerous to eat something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So first of all, we were looking for medication.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew it-- we knew it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The danger was in the camp to get dysentery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means a death.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were looking for the train with medication.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There are many, many wagons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember even the name of the medication, which was, at that time, against dysentery was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we ate a lot of [NON-ENGLISH] before we ate something else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We found a lot of food there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was it after--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was, more or less, in this-- at this time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't tell you exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was the first time after--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we came, as I told you, to a-- again, to a camp, from where most of them went to the Russian side, then they went till Slovakia and slowly reached, after a couple of weeks, Prague.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no other way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We two children wrote a list-- pro and contra-- what will happen if we run away from the camp-- it was now after the war-- and go straight on our own, and what will happen if we don't.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we know if don't, it will be-- we have to go again, all this with a group and with the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if we do it by our own, we have a chance, maybe a little better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that what we choose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We somehow escaped, went by our own to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, there, we went to the Czech consul.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, in Vienna, the first repatriation cars left from Prague, let's say, once or twice in a-- in a week.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all these repatriation people who went back and forwards, were actually black market people.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
